# Hotel detail page — CDC §2 architecture (15 blocs)

This page is the **strategic surface** that competes against Booking, Hotels.com and the official hotel website. CDC v3.0 §2 defines 15 mandatory blocks. A PR that touches `/hotel/[slug]/page.tsx` must visit this checklist.

## Decisions (do not relitigate without an ADR)

| Décision | Référence |
|---|---|
